</div>

<div class="cv-body">
  <div></div>
  <div>
  <ul>
    <li>Designed user-friendly graphical interfaces using C#, WPF, and Prism under MVVM software architectural patterns.</li>
    <li>Implemented Ethernet-based PLC communication protocols to structure messages between PC softwares and the PLC runtime systems.</li>
    <li>Learned to develop PLC programs in TwinCAT, including implementing control logic in IEC 61131-3 languages, configuring I/O mapping, and testing execution through simulations.</li>
  </ul>
  <div class="cv-subhead">Key Achievements & Skills Developed:</div>
  <ul>
    <li>Applied C# programming to real-world software development, strengthening problem-solving and implementation skills.</li>
    <li>Gained hands-on experience in controlling PLC simulations and hardware systems.</li>
    <li>Expanded computer science foundations and expertise in modular design, system operations, and applied engineering contexts, complementing academic research in linguistics.</li>
  </ul>
  </div>
</div>
```

## Professional Skills

-   **Languages:** Mandarin (Native); English (Proficient); Spanish (Intermediate); Hebrew (Basic)
-   **Skills:** Python (Advanced); C (Intermediate); C# (Basic); R (Basic); Markup Languages: HTML, XML, XAML (Basic); JavaScript (Fundamental).
-   **Interests:** Language learning (e.g., Spanish, Hebrew), Programming Language, Theatre, Singing, etc.

